---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Created: Sender signs event
    Created --> Queued: Edge Agent validates + queues
    Queued --> Relaying: Transport adapter sends

    state Relaying {
        [*] --> Hop1: First relay
        Hop1 --> HopN: Store-and-forward
        HopN --> Delivered: Recipient in range
        HopN --> Cached: No path, TTL > 0
        Cached --> HopN: New neighbor discovered
    }

    Relaying --> Delivered: Target node receives
    Relaying --> Expired: TTL exhausted

    Delivered --> Executing: Payload is executable
    Delivered --> Fulfilled: Data-only event

    Executing --> ProofGenerated: zkVM generates receipt
    ProofGenerated --> Committed: Commit Node batches

    Committed --> Anchored: Bitcoin L2 settlement
    Anchored --> Settled: L1 anchoring (periodic)

    Expired --> [*]
    Fulfilled --> [*]
    Settled --> [*]
